<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request - Qubide</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
                <table role="presentation" width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                    style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
                    <!-- Header -->
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center"
                            style="padding: 30px 0 30px; background-color: #003366; border-top-left-radius: 8px; border-top-right-radius: 8px;">
                            <img src="{{logo}}" alt="Qubide Logo" style="max-width: 80px; height: auto; border-radius: 4px;">
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <!-- Content -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0 30px;">
                            <h1 style="color: #003366; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Hello {{name}},
                            </h1>
                            <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">We
                                received a request to reset the password for your Qubide account. Here are
                                the details:</p>
                            <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">To reset
                                your password, please click the button below:</p>
                            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                                <tr>
                                    <td align="center">
                                        <a href="{{resetLink}}"
                                            style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #009933; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">Reset
                                            Your Password</a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                            <p
                                style="color: #ff0000; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 20px; font-style: italic;">
                                Important: This password reset link is valid for 5 minutes. If you don't reset your
                                password within this time, you'll need to submit a new request.</p>
                            <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 30px;">If you
                                didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact our IT support team
                                immediately if you believe this is an unauthorized attempt to access your account.</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>